ita Br\u00f6llochs","affiliation":"Friedrich-Alexander-Universit\u00e4t in Erlangen, Germany","username":"anita-brllochs","email":"mbrown@chanzuckerberg.com","pa_useranme":"max-brown","comments":[]},"is_project":0}]},{"id":"602551","is_changed":"0","original_id":"0","is_skipped":"0","is_checked":"0","guid":"060E4E34D4D0472C80BC20F2415CEAB5","previous_guid":"8C5704D4E3FB4070B498B1189D528B3C","previous_id":"602550","last_modified":"1515698363","components":[{"component_id":"1041659","previous_id":0,"original_id":"0","guid":"AD9D7739B3DA4D69BF7DEB64AB425212","previous_guid":null,"component_type_id":"6","data_id":"0","data":"","order_id":"0","name":"Section","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"6","source_data":{"section":""},"is_project":0},{"component_id":"1041658","previous_id":"1041659","original_id":"0","guid":"664E4EE014324ED49AEE8959E5701ED6","previous_guid":"AD9D7739B3DA4D69BF7DEB64AB425212","component_type_id":"1","data_id":null,"data":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Connect all tubing to the appropriate channels in the microfluidic device, and generate droplets.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","order_id":"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Connect all tubing to the appropriate channels in the microfluidic device, and generate droplets.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>"},"is_project":0}]},{"id":"602552","is_changed":"0","original_id":"0","is_skipped":"0","is_checked":"0","guid":"E276768B73ED41B2877666E66D8606C6","previous_guid":"060E4E34D4D0472C80BC20F2415CEAB5","previous_id":"602551","last_modified":"1515698358","components":[{"component_id":"1041661","previous_id":0,"original_id":"0","guid":"5753DE3739C84BEFAA3C63AAF97941CB","previous_guid":null,"component_type_id":"6","data_id":"0","data":"","order_id":"0","name":"Section","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"6","source_data":{"section":""},"is_project":0},{"component_id":"1041660","previous_id":"1041661","original_id":"0","guid":"4C72CB4B941947FF8FCC134BE3E367A9","previous_guid":"5753DE3739C84BEFAA3C63AAF97941CB","component_type_id":"1","data_id":null,"data":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For a given number of droplets, count the number of beads inside. You should count the beads inside several hundred droplets to make sure that you have a statistically sound estimate.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","order_id":"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">For a given number of droplets, count the number of beads inside. You should count the beads inside several hundred droplets to make sure that you have a statistically sound estimate.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>"},"is_project":0}]},{"id":"602553","is_changed":"0","original_id":"0","is_skipped":"0","is_checked":"0","guid":"1712BC56A4CF40478D517C7E325D58CF","previous_guid":"E276768B73ED41B2877666E66D8606C6","previous_id":"602552","last_modified":"1515698433","components":[{"component_id":"1041663","previous_id":0,"original_id":"0","guid":"9B23B15BC14A49EC80E1E858722E033C","previous_guid":null,"component_type_id":"6","data_id":"0","data":"","order_id":"0","name":"Section","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"6","source_data":{"section":""},"is_project":0},{"component_id":"1041662","previous_id":"1041663","original_id":"0","guid":"77B7FA4208AF466E997000176C4CCA8C","previous_guid":"9B23B15BC14A49EC80E1E858722E033C","component_type_id":"1","data_id":null,"data":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Divide the total number of beads counted inside droplets by the number of droplets you counted. This is your <strong>droplet occupancy<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","order_id":"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Divide the total number of beads counted inside droplets by the number of droplets you counted. This is your <strong>droplet occupancy<\/strong>.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>"},"is_project":0}]},{"id":"602555","is_changed":"0","original_id":"0","is_skipped":"0","is_checked":"0","guid":"7F287F784CDA41249DB5FF51A6B88830","previous_guid":"1712BC56A4CF40478D517C7E325D58CF","previous_id":"602553","last_modified":"1515698457","components":[{"component_id":"1041667","previous_id":0,"original_id":"0","guid":"B97D8FFF5315481BA6477A6350908DF4","previous_guid":null,"component_type_id":"6","data_id":"0","data":"","order_id":"0","name":"Section","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"6","source_data":{"section":""},"is_project":0},{"component_id":"1041666","previous_id":"1041667","original_id":"0","guid":"5B0D3B6732404B4D957F18F176C29918","previous_guid":"B97D8FFF5315481BA6477A6350908DF4","component_type_id":"1","data_id":null,"data":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>Here is how to calculate droplet volume:<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><em>Droplet volume = (\u200bdroplet occupancy\u200b) \/ (500 beads per microliter ) = # microliters per droplet.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>","order_id":"1","name":"Description","data_by_id":"0","type_id":"1","source_data":{"description":"<div title=\"Page 1\">\n<div>\n<div>\n<div>\n<p>Here is how to calculate droplet volume:<\/p>\n<p>\u00a0<\/p>\n<p><em>Droplet volume = (\u200bdroplet occupancy\u200b) \/ (500 beads per microliter ) = # microliters per droplet.<\/em><\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>"},"is_project":0}]}]}